summary: My work in progress ENB preset.
descriptionHtml:
I don't have much to say here but I'm new to making my own ENB and this is the first mod I have ever uploaded to Nexus.

If there are any problems with my ENB or this page please let me know.

[size=3][b][i][u]If you don't know how to install an ENB preset please go learn how on YouTube.

[/u][/i][/b][/size]This ENB is very hard for me to run so I assume the same will be for you.

This ENB [color=#ffff00][u]requires[/u][/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30450/?]Realistic Lighting Overhaul[/url].

Due to what I believe is a bug please use ENB 0.262 because 0.264 causes me to crash on loading screens.

Update: [color=#ff0000][u][b][i]As of 02/10/2014 there is now a performance version with some effects disabled and modified. It should for the most part look identicle but obviously with some stuff turned off.[/i][/b][/u][/color]
author: Kilobytez95
